## ğŸš€ **Installation & Setup**
### 1ï¸âƒ£ **Clone the Repository**
```sh
git clone https://github.com/your-repo/ecommerce-microservices.git
cd ecommerce-microservices
```

---

### 2ï¸âƒ£ **Setup Backend**
#### ğŸ“Œ **Create Database**
Open MySQL and run:
```sql
CREATE DATABASE ecommerce_db;
```

#### ğŸ“Œ **Configure `application.properties`**
Modify `backend/user-service/src/main/resources/application.properties`:

```
spring.datasource.url=jdbc:mysql://localhost:3306/ecommerce_db
spring.datasource.username=root
spring.datasource.password=password
spring.datasource.driver-class-name=com.mysql.cj.jdbc.Driver
spring.jpa.hibernate.ddl-auto=update
```

#### ğŸ“Œ **Run Backend Services**
Open separate terminals and run:

```sh
cd backend/user-service
mvn spring-boot:run
```

```sh
cd backend/product-service
mvn spring-boot:run
```

```sh
cd backend/order-service
mvn spring-boot:run
```

```sh
cd backend/gateway-service
mvn spring-boot:run
```

---

### 3ï¸âƒ£ **Setup Frontend**
#### ğŸ“Œ **Install Dependencies**
```sh
cd frontend
npm install
```

#### ğŸ“Œ **Run Frontend**
```sh
npm start
```

The app should be running at:  
ğŸ‘‰ **http://localhost:3000**

---

## ğŸ”¥ **API Endpoints**
| Method | Endpoint               | Description              |
|--------|------------------------|--------------------------|
| GET    | `/api/products`        | Get all products        |
| GET    | `/api/products/{id}`   | Get product by ID       |
| POST   | `/api/orders`          | Place an order         |
| GET    | `/api/orders/{userId}` | Get user orders        |

---

## ğŸ“¦ **Build & Deployment**
### ğŸ“Œ **Build Frontend**
```sh
npm run build
```

### ğŸ“Œ **Serve with Spring Boot**
Move `frontend/build/` to `backend/gateway-service/static/` and modify `application.properties`:

```
spring.web.resources.static-locations=classpath:/static/
```

### ğŸ“Œ **Run Everything**
```sh
mvn package && java -jar target/gateway-service.jar
```

